snippet.title: Troublemaker IndieGoGo Trailer
snippet.description:
Back Now! - https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/troublemaker

Troublemaker: Raise Your Gang is a 3rd person action-adventure game set in Indonesia’s greatest combat arena: High School! 

Play as Budi, a new transfer student at Cipta Wiyata High in Jayakarta. You and your family have moved to Jayakarta so that you could attend this prestigious vocational school. (...And because you got into too many fights at your previous school!)
